article:
On 27-Mar-2018, 8 CC cameras were installed in the premises of Sree Sunama Jakini and Malkuma Jakini maata temple in Gooty town. We take this opportunity to congratulate and thank the donors who has supported us unconditionally to achieve this task.
We look forward to have the same support and encouragement from Sunama Jakini maatha devotees in our future developmental activities.
Follow the official Sunama Jakini Maatha Channel at YouTube
